  "description": "From the manufacturer Skulls The skull, symbolic of death and mortality, is a well-loved ornament in households all over the world. Whether used as a quirky centrepiece or to add a dark twist to an otherwise normal space, Skulls are an amazing decorative piece. Draculas Tale Convincingly realistic, this skull sports a pair of pointed canines, ready to puncture your skin and drain your blood! Cast in the finest resin before being expertly hand-painted, this skull would make the perfect addition to any horror collection. The Aristocrat Grinning merrily, this skull wears an elegant top hat with a stylish brown feather in it. Sitting atop, the brim is a pair of brass goggles. Brass cog work crawls across the hat next to them. Spirit Board Skull Encompassing the black cranium is Nemesis Now's Spirit Board design, decorated with white baroque detailing on the handle base and rim. In the centre, the alphabet is marked out in an arc. The design also includes numbers 0 to 9 and the words YES and NO.",
